{{!< default}}

{{> "headers/header-vat"}}

<main id="vat" class="vat" role="main">

    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col s12">
            <div class="card" style="padding: 20px;">
                <h2 class="_te-ac">VAT Info Request</h2>
                <h6 class="_te-ac font__subtitle">Need a price quote?</h6>
                <p style="padding-top: 20px;">
                We know that handling VAT for yacht charters can be time consuming, difficult and costly.  That's why we're here to help make it a smooth and efficient process.  If you would like us to send you a price quote and brief outline of how we can handle your VAT needs, please fill out this request form.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The size of your vessel does NOT matter. Our knowledgeable staff will handle all of your VAT matters in Croatia.
                </p>
                <div style="text-align: center; width: 100%;">
                <a class="waves-effect waves-light btn modal__button modal__button--dark" href="#modal--tax-form">VAT Request</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row" style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <div class="col s12 m6">
            <div class="card card--full" href="#">
                <div class="card-image">
                    <img src="{{asset "images/pages/vat/vat-1.jpg"}}" />
                    <div class="card-overlay"></div>
                    <span class="card-title">VAT FAQs</span>
                </div>
                <div class="card-reveal">
                    <div class="card-reveal-inner">
                        <div class="card-line"></div>
                        <p><span class="list-highlight">1.</span>Which yachts can legally perform charters in Croaita?</p>
                        <p style="padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 5px;">Any commercial or pleasure yachts which are:</p>
                        <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                            <li>EU flagged yachts, of any size</li>
                            <li>Non EU flagged yachts with a LOA of 40m and up, if they obtain a charter license</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p><span class="list-highlight">2.</span> As a yacht owner, can I perform a legal charter business in Croatia?</p>
                        <p style="padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 5px;">The short answer is yes, but you must do 1 of these 2 things to be legal:</p>
                        <ul style="padding-left: 20px;">
                            <li>Open a charter company in Croatia, or</li>
                            <li>Appoint a charter representative</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p style="padding-left: 20px;">
                            You must also obtain a Value Added Tax (VAT) number (VAT ID) along with a Croatian Personal Identification Number (PIN)
                        </p>
                        <div class="card-line"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col s12 m6">
            <div class="card card--full" href="#">
                <div class="card-image">
                    <img src="{{asset "images/pages/vat/vat-2.jpg"}}">
                    {{!--<div class="card-overlay"></div>--}}
                    {{!--<span class="card-title">Easytax Partnership</span>--}}
                </div>
                    <div class="card-reveal">
                        <div>
                        <div class="card-line"></div>
                        <p>
                            We've partnered with Easytax of France to assist yachts throughout the Med
                        </p>
                        <div class="card-line"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

</main>

<!-- Modal Structure -->
<div id="modal--tax-form" class="modal bottom-sheet">
    <div class="modal-content">
        {{> "social/yacht-tax-form"}}
    </div>
</div>

{{> "footer"}}
